        <ul class="checkbox">
            <li>
                <img src="../../Images/TestPlans/Buttons/Button---ShowLineNumbers.png" style="mc-tag-and-class: ;" /><span class="bold">(Show line numbers): </span>Shows or hides numbered lines in the <span class="UI">Text Editor</span>.</li>
            <li>
                <img src="../../Images/TestPlans/Buttons/Button---ShowOutline.png" style="mc-tag-and-class: ;" /><span class="bold">(Show outline): </span>Shows or hides small minus and plus buttons next to lines with tags. These let you collapse or expand those portions of the code.</li>
            <li>
                <img src="../../Images/TestPlans/Buttons/Button---ShowSyntaxColor.png" style="mc-tag-and-class: ;" /><span class="bold">(Show syntax colors):&#160;</span>Shows or hides syntax coloring in the <span class="UI">Text Editor</span>.</li>
            <li>
                <img src="../../Images/TestPlans/Buttons/Button---WordWrap.png" style="mc-tag-and-class: ;" /><span class="bold">(Word wrap): </span>Turns on wrapping in the editor to eliminate the need for horizontal scrolling.</li>
            <li>
                <img src="../../Images/TestPlans/Buttons/Button---ToggleAutoComplete.png" style="mc-tag-and-class: ;" /><span class="bold">(Toggle Auto Complete):&#160;</span>Enables or disables the auto complete functionality in the <span class="UI">Text Editor</span>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>&#160;</p>
